[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12493] switched the CI to use macOS-13 instead of macOS-latest, due to failures
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12439] added a 
``GetSpanContents``
 engine call
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12437] isolated tests from user config
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12410] added a 
``--no-newline``
 option to 
``nu``
